mary-700\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div>ABC<span class=\"text-accent-500\">Resolve</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#como-funciona\">Como funciona</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#categorias\">Serviços</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Pedir orçamento</a></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"btn-accent text-sm py-2\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço</a><a class=\"btn-secondary text-sm py-2\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Sou prestador</a></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"bg-gray-50 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 mb-6\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg> Voltar</a><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-10\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Cadastre-se como prestador</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 mb-8\">Comece a receber pedidos de clientes na sua região. Gratuito para começar.</p><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900\">Perfil verificado</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">Seu cadastro é analisado pela nossa equipe.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900\">Avaliações visíveis</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">Clientes veem suas avaliações antes de contratar.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900\">Receba pedidos 24h</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">Notificações de novos clientes na sua área.</p></div></div></div></div><form class=\"md:col-span-3 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm space-y-5\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div class=\"sm:col-span-2\"><label class=\"label\">Nome completo *</label><input class=\"input\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"João Silva\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">E-mail *</label><input class=\"input\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"joao@email.com\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Telefone *</label><input class=\"input\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"(11) 99999-9999\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">WhatsApp</label><input class=\"input\" placeholder=\"(11) 99999-9999\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Cidade *</label><select class=\"input\" required=\"\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Selecione...</option><option value=\"Santo André\">Santo André</option><option value=\"São Bernardo do Campo\">São Bernardo do Campo</option><option value=\"São Caetano do Sul\">São Caetano do Sul</option><option value=\"Diadema\">Diadema</option><option value=\"Mauá\">Mauá</option><option value=\"Ribeirão Pires\">Ribeirão Pires</option><option value=\"Rio Grande da Serra\">Rio Grande da Serra</option></select></div><div><label class=\"label\">Bairro</label><input class=\"input\" placeholder=\"Seu bairro\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Área de atuação *</label><select class=\"input\" required=\"\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Selecione...</option></select></div><div><label class=\"label\">Anos de experiência</label><select class=\"input\"><option value=\"0\" selected=\"\">Menos de 1 ano</option><option value=\"1\">1 ano</option><option value=\"2\">2 anos</option><option value=\"3\">3 anos</option><option value=\"5\">5 anos</option><option value=\"10\">10+ anos</option></select></div><div class=\"sm:col-span-2\"><label class=\"label\">Descreva seus serviços *</label><textarea class=\"input resize-none h-32\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Ex: Eletricista com 10 anos de experiência em instalações residenciais e comerciais. Especializado em ar-condicionado, quadros elétricos e iluminação.\"></textarea><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1\">Descreva sua experiência e os serviços que oferece.</p></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary w-full py-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-base\">Enviar cadastro</button><p class=\"text-center text-xs text-gray-400\">Ao enviar, você concorda com nossos <a class=\"underline\" href=\"/termos\">termos de uso</a>. Análise em até 48h.</p></form></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-extrabold text-xl text-white mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91